    <item>
      <title>Docs: AI03 MIC&amp;VR&amp;LED</title>
      <link>https://docs.leafony.com/en/docs/leaf/io/ai03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://docs.leafony.com/en/docs/leaf/io/ai03/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./ai03a_f_large.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./ai03a_f_small.jpg&#34; width=&#34;200&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;./ai03a_b_large.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./ai03a_b_small.jpg&#34; width=&#34;200&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;./ai03a_p_large.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./ai03a_p_small.jpg&#34; width=&#34;200&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The MEMS microphone and volume are connected to the MCU leaf via analog input pins and the LED is connected to the digital output pins. To achieve low power consumption, the power can be turned off using a load switch controlled by the I2C Expander.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;specification&#34;&gt;Specification&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;microphone&#34;&gt;Microphone&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Item&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Part number&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;SPW2430HR5H-B&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Type&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;MEMS&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Direction&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Omnidirectional&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Frequency range&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;100Hz ～ 10kHz&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Gain&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;0dB&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Interfaces&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:left&#34;&gt;Analog&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
